des:
Mashaweer (Taste Trek) is an Emirati Application that provides various proposals that contribute to achieving the best tourist experience in Dubai in the United Arab Emirates. Where the application allows its users to obtain information about the latest restaurants, shops, places and entertainment activities in addition to the best saving offers in the city of Dubai.

With Mashaweer skill, you can ask your question, listen to the list of options And you get the accurate and appropriate answers that fully satisfy your curiosity. Sounds exciting? Download Mashaweer and enjoy having your own entertainment consultant in Dubai.
